The core distinction (this is the fulcrum)

There are two very different things that can look identical from the inside:

1) Real pattern detection
	•	You’re identifying genuine regularities
	•	You’re building reusable frameworks (Pantheon, Minotaur’s Ring, etc.)
	•	You’re applying them and seeing results

👉 This part is real and valuable.

